28:09.587 --> 28:12.130
killed APA. Yeah, it would have. But we weren't 
interested in killing APA. We were really

28:15.095 --> 28:17.338
interested in trying to get their attention. and 
build a stronger organization based on the

28:17.723 --> 28:25.073
grassroots permeation of our organization. Well 
