28:41.483 --> 28:44.345
year. Next year, Jim Duncan will assume a chapter 
of the national presidency. And Jim has this

28:49.170 --> 28:55.595
chapter bias, this action orientation, the 
culture of the consumer business philosophy. And

28:56.136 --> 28:59.939
you will see the organization become much more 
responsive next year. As this labor element

29:00.079 --> 29:06.985
dissipates, the housekeeping of Krumholz will 
consume this year. And then Jim will really have a

29:07.506 --> 29:10.208
stage set for him to get in there And also the big 
change is that Jim will have a two-year term. That

29:14.306 --> 29:17.410
was one of the other changes we made in our 
amendment process. We revised our charter. That

29:18.632 --> 29:20.154
makes a lot of sense. Longer term in office. One 
